{"tid":2498213,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[抗分化] 發現五毛喺抗爭/行動po嘅兩個特徵","createTime":"2021-04-21T04:24:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T08:16:25.000Z","uid":258706,"like":18,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"418f0d143499c6cb3578f48ddfd5949e3d187cb5","tid":2498213,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T04:24:45.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"small\"><span class=\"red\">以下只係我嘅發現，唔代表數據必定準確，亦唔係鼓吹大家捉鬼</span></span><br />\n先唔論反修例運動究竟完咗未，發現呢排好多po只要討論<span class=\"gold\">香港靠乜方法得以重光</span>或涉及<span class=\"gold\">任何抗爭行動</span>，都會有堆明顯唔符合黃營主流意見嘅五毛入去<span class=\"pink\">搞分化、引罵戰</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 務求要搞到大家放棄彼此尊重，忘卻各自努力<br />\n<br />\n 而嗰啲會被負評到成千個dislike嘅留言，有以下特徵：<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">特徵一：<span class=\"teal\">用諧音諷刺手足</span></span><br />\n用一大堆藍媒、親中政黨用嘅諷刺字眼去譏笑手足<br />\n包括：<br />\n <span class=\"gold\">良知</span>&rarr;<span class=\"blue\">糧支</span><br />\ne.g. 班區議員係為咗<span class=\"blue\">糧支</span>先進入議會咋嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲話要DQ前搞集會支持佢哋<br />\n <span class=\"gold\">手足</span>&rarr;<span class=\"blue\">手joke</span><br />\ne.g. 啲手joke喺倉底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢就走撚咗去美國嘆世界 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">特徵二：<span class=\"teal\">你條撚樣</span></span><br />\n發現唔少抗爭po會有好多提及&ldquo;<span class=\"blue\">你條撚樣</span>&rdquo;嘅留言出現，包括<span class=\"orange\">遊行po</span>、<span class=\"orange\">義士流亡po</span>、<span class=\"orange\">建立海外組織po</span><br />\ne.g. 仲搞遊行？<span class=\"blue\">你條撚樣</span>又想推班後生去送頭<br />\ne.g. 特朗普輸撚咗喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"blue\">你條撚樣</span>仲覺得求美國有用 ？？<br />\n<br />\n明明打&ldquo;你&rdquo;字咁方便，仲要加多三個字<br />\n有時一個po得幾十個留言但仲要有6、7個<span class=\"blue\">你條撚樣</span>嘅留言，有冇咁啱咁橋呢？<br />\n<br />\n講到尾，希望大家都係<span class=\"gold\">互相尊重</span>，喺一個未揾到解決到破局方法之時，多一份包容，唔好俾五毛牽動到情緖同譏諷提出建議未必一定Work嘅同路人 <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">不割蓆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不批鬥</span></span>"},{"pid":"713de04ac14a8f8af073941b548a675808de7ce6","tid":2498213,"uid":267410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T04:25:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fb8024430714cbf79e38cd7071716b359e85c71","tid":2498213,"uid":188252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T04:27:06.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2bc673231509aa22017fcc97918d3629c443f8","tid":2498213,"uid":37719,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T04:29:06.000Z","msg":"論做五毛一定係開盲撐post<br />\n睇下林家謙，如果我開個post屌佢，你唔知咩事可能會冇咩feel，如果我開個post屈佢內向，拉到既仇恨值一定大10倍"},{"pid":"3782955a2a2e6874658fff68b9fa84341b0f586f","tid":2498213,"uid":89182,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T04:29:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmf3F4eDsrerkp1Xdj6b7sbST1wZRq45pTM8H5MTFkNoB6?filename=XQubp53.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXQubp53.gif&h=d1de8349&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f9e2acf6d093b15c6887509e3ad01bbd8bc9a7a","tid":2498213,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T04:32:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c9912cc94ef7c236ea3eb203e805dd144673064","tid":2498213,"uid":289946,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T04:33:43.000Z","msg":"行動post係邊？睇過？😂"},{"pid":"f87452627cc137244247894f39ef676145e0974a","tid":2498213,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T04:35:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.